{"type":null,"faqId":48009,"title":"输入文本","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.19722222in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.td1{width:0.82708335in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid black;border-left:thin solid black;border-right:thin solid black;border-top:thin solid black;}\n.td2{width:4.6854167in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid black;border-left:thin solid black;border-right:thin solid black;border-top:thin solid black;}\n.r1{keep-together:always;}\n.t1{table-layout:fixed;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>输入文本前，点击文本框，屏幕键盘会自动开启。输入结束后，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177714\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”关闭屏幕键盘。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">华为输入法</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>左右滑动键盘面板，可以在全键盘和九键盘界面之间切换。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177715\" style=\"width:3.6631944in;height:1.8333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<table class=\"t1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177716\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>对输入法进行个性化设置，如更换输入法皮肤、调节键盘高度等。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177717\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>在中文输入法界面，点击可在大写字母锁定输入和中文输入间切换。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>在英文输入法界面，点击可在大写字母输入和小写字母输入间切换，双击可切换为大写字母锁定输入。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177718\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>输入数字和符号。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177719\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>在中文输入键盘和英文输入键盘间切换。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177720\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>输入标点或表情符号。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177721\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击输入列表中的符号。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>长按进入符号列表编辑界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>向上拖动列表，点击</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177722\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>可在列表中增加符号。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177723\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>移动光标或对文本进行选取、剪切、复制和粘贴等操作。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177724\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>切换输入法或键盘。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177725\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>切换到语音输入模式。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">华为手写输入法</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177726\" style=\"width:3.6666667in;height:2.417361in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<table class=\"t1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177727\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>在半屏手写或全屏手写间切换。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177728\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>手写区域。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177729\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>输入数字。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177730\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>输入标点或表情符号。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177731\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>输入表情图标。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177732\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>切换输入法和键盘。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<span>“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177733\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>切换到语音输入模式。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">编辑文本</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"编辑文字\"XE \"选取文字\"XE \"选择文字\"XE \"复制文字\"XE \"剪切文字\"XE \"粘贴文本\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"编辑文本\"您可以对文本进行选取、剪切、复制和粘贴等操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177734\" style=\"width:3.1583333in;height:1.6666666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>XE \"选取文本\"</span><span class=\"s1\">选取文本</span><span>：长按文字区域，直至出现“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177735\" style=\"width:0.18055555in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，拖动“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177736\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”和“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177737\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”选择要编辑的文本，或点击“全选”选择全部文字。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>XE \"复制文本\"</span><span class=\"s1\">复制文本</span><span>：选取文本后，点击“复制”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>XE \"剪切文本\"</span><span class=\"s1\">剪切文本</span><span>：选取文本后，点击“剪切”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>XE \"粘贴文本\"</span><span class=\"s1\">粘贴文本</span><span>：长按选择文本插入点，点击“粘贴”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177738\" style=\"width:3.2305555in;height:1.6666666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<br>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n<div  >\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1090,"faqType":"开始使用","useful":6,"unUseful":5,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3595","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Getting-know-phone","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598086000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":144,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}